column5: The muskie wondergod, will swing by Dave Mercers booth for our OFC Meet, Greet and BLEEP!!  Saturday at 1:00 at Dave's booth across from the seminar section!  OFC - often replicated ... never duplicated!!!
Cool, so now I have to figure out how to keep the kids happy till then... Geoff
Dang!  I wish I could be there Saturday.
Lookin' forward to it TJ. Sounds like a blast. Look forward to seeing lots of OFNER's and meeting Dave  Pete
Don't forget the hat's Pete...
:thumbsup_anim:yippy!!!!
Hats?
Yes Hats Pete, lots of hat
OH I thought they meant the HAT
Man. No more drinkin' and surfin' for me.
Yikes!!!!  Did anyone tell show management that guy was showin' up?
I dunno if I can make it Pete :-( You can give my hat to TJ though! That would be nice...otherwise, I'll see you in the summer.

Whadduya mean you can't make it Roy? No excuses (you just want to sneak in quietly for your pink hat eh   )  Gotta admit, "Mainarella" is pretty good stuff ... you sawed-off, kilt-wearing weirdo.  You recognize it so well 'cuz that's your kilt Terry put on me.  Can't wait to go to the ball ... sounding more like a costume party all the time.
So how many of us are actually meeting up at the booth on saterday? Do we have a head count?
I was going Saturday, but with all this macho dress wearing going on I may have to postpone till sunday
Coward. When in doubt, don't hug or kiss anybody.  JF
Looks like these guys are gonna have a ball together Terra Del Fuego ,here I come  One might think its the Ice Capades,stars on ice!  hahahahahahahahaha  Tks Terry  Bwahahahahahahahahahahahahahaha

Jealousy is a viscious thing my friend  You'll be wishing you were there, with a pink furry hat.  Oh come on dude, don't cancel on Sat. (Sound advice from John there   ) ... show up and be certain to bring your camera.  Heading out in the morning ... looking forward to seeing you all.  Pete
Oh man that is TOOOO FUNNY!!!!!!  good one Marc and Terry  See you all on Sat.  Geoff
Awe man!! I wish I could go Saturday - but I can't!  I'm going MONDAY tho.....if that counts for anything!

Dude I am going ice fishing on Saturday My only concern is seeing all 3 of you showing up all decked out  Jealousy .... why? I slept in a Holiday Express Inn  I think the show should use the pic in their add campaign,sure to draw a crowd  Fishing Pals  I just love Terry work

AHHHH HA HA HA HA!!!! I love these pictures!!!!!  I just wanted everyone to know I am having some new styles of Pink fuzzy hats made up!!! I will let you know when they are ready.  I am starting to think I should be having some TuTus made for you boys too!!!  -Jen www.PeteMaina.com
